   <category name='moves'>

      <section name='keepout'>

         <para number='1' comment='Turn back non-staff'>
         As you walk away from your shuttle, a figure in a white environmental suit hurries up to you. "No, stop right there," he says. "Sorry, we've got a bit of a contamination problem at the moment, you have to leave." He pushes you back towards your shuttle and won't allow you to go anywhere else.
         </para>

